The FOTA Manager (FotaMgr) controls the Firmware Over The Air (FOTA) Client on the device, which allows administrators to update Zebra devices remotely by sending configurations to the device over the air. 

### Main Functionality

* Set the State (active/inactive) of the FOTA Client on the device 
* Enable/disable the FOTA user interface on the device

